nSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010050, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay soonne waalo’n se ziyadah soonne waale, ay dekhne waalo’n se ziyadah dekhne waale, ay hisaab karne waalo’n mein tez-tar, ay sab se bade haakim, ay khalq shudah cheezo’n ke khaaliq, ay rizq paane waalo’n ke raaziq, ay madad-yaafta logo’n ke madad-gaar, ay sab se badh kar rahem karne waale, ay pareshaan logo’n ke rehnuma, ay faryaadiyo’n ke faryaad-ras meri faryaad-rasi kar.", "Urdu": "شکر ہے خدا کے لیے۔", "RArabic": "YAA ASMA-A’S SAAME-EE’NA YAA AB-SARAN NAAZE-REENA YAA ASRA-A’L HAASE-BEENA YAA AH-KAMAL HAAKE-MEENA YAA KHAALE-QAL MAKHLOO-QEENA YAA RAAZE-QAL MARZOO-QEENA YAA NAASE-RAL MANSOO-REENA YAA AR-HAMAR-RAAHE-MEENA YAA DALEE-LAL MOTA-HAIYYE-REENA YAA GHEYAA-SAL MUS-TAGHEE-SEENA AGHIS-NEE.", "ArabicText1": "يَا اَسْمَعَ السَّامِعِيْنَ يَا اَبْصَرَ النَّاظِرِيْنَ يَا اَسْرَعَ الْحَاسِبِيْنَ يَا اَحْكَمَ الْحَاكِمِيْنَ يَا خَالِقَ الْمَخْلُوْقِيْنَ يَا رَازِقَ الْمَرْزُوْقِيْنَ يَا نَاصِرَ الْمَنْصُوْرِيْنَ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ يَا دَلِيْلَ الْمُتَحَيِّرِيْنَ يَا غِيَاثَ الْمُسْتَغِيْثِيْنَ اَغِثْنِيْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010051, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay yaum'e jaza o saza ke maalik, ham Teri hi ibaadat karte hai aur Tujhi se madad maangte hai, ay dukh-yaaro’n ke faryaad-ras, ay dua qabool karne waale Tu hi woh Allah hai jo aalameen ka Parwardigaar hai, Tu hi woh Allah hai keh Tere siwa koi ma’bood nahi, Tu sachcha aur haqeeqee hukm-raan hai keh badaayi Tera libaas hai.", "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "YAA MAALE-KA YAWMID DEENE AIYYA-KA NA’BODO WA IYYAA-KA NASTA-EE’NO YAA SAREE-KHAL MAKROO-BEENA YAA MOJEE-BA DA’WATIL MUZTA-REENA ANTAL LAAHO RABBUL AA’LA-MEENA ANTAL LAAHO LAA ILAAHA ILLAA ANTAL MALE-KUL HAQQUL MOBEE-NUL KIBRE-YAA-O REDAA-OKA.", "ArabicText1": "يَا مَالِكَ يَوْمِ الدِّيْنِ اِيَّاكَ نَعْبُدُ وَاِيَّاكَ نَسْتَعِيْنُ يَا صَرِيْخَ الْمَكْرُوْبِيْنَ يَا مُجِيْبَ دَعْوَةِ الْمُضْطَرِّيْنَ اَنْتَ اللهُ رَبُّ الْعَالَمِيْنَ اَنْتَ اللهُ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اَنْتَ الْمَلِكُ الْحَقُّ الْمُبِيْنُ الْكِبْرِيَاءُ رِدَاؤُكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010052, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood Muhammad'e Mustafa (s.a.w.a) par rehmat naazil farma, aur Ali'e Murtaza (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma, aur Fatema Zahra (s.a) aur Khadeejatul Kubra (s.a) par rehmat naazil farma, aur Hasan'e Mujtabah (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma, aur us Husain (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma jo Karbala mein shaheed huwe, aur Ali ibne Husain Zainul Aabedin (a.s) aur Muhammad'e Baqir (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma, aur Jafar'e Sadiq (a.s) aur Moosa'e Kazim (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma, aur Ali'e Reza (a.s) aur Muhammad'e Taqi (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma, aur Ali'e Naqi (a.s) aur Hasan'e Askari (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma, aur Hujjat'e Qaaem Imam Mahdi (a.t.f.s) par rehmat naazil farma, Khuda ki rehmate’n ho un sab par.", "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADE-NIL MUSTAFAA, WA A’LAA A’LIYYIL MURTAZAA, WA FAATEMA-TAZ ZAHRAA-E, WA KHADEEJA-TAL KUBRAA, WAL HASANIL MUJTABAA, WAL HUSAI-NISH SHAHEEDE BE-KARBALAA-A, WA A’LAA A’LIYYIB-NIL HUSAINE ZAIY-NIL AA’BE-DEENA, WA MOHAMMA-DIB-NE ALIYYI-NIL BAAQERE, WA JA’FA-RIB-NE MOHAMMADIS SAADEQE, WA MOO-SAB-NE JA’FARE-NIL KAAZEME, WA A’LIYYIB-NE MOOSAR REZAA, WA MOHAMMA-DIB-NE ALIYYE-NIT TAQIYYE, WA A’LIY-YIB-NE MOHAMMADIN NAQIYYE, WAL HASA-NIB-NE ALIYYI-NIL A’S-KARIYYE, WAL HUJJA-TIL QAAA'e MIL MAHDIY-YIL IMAAMIL MUNTA-ZARE SALWAA-TUL LAAHE A’LAIY-HIM AJMA-EE’NA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": " نِ", "ArabicText2": "الْمُصْطَفٰى وَعَلٰى عَلِيٍّ الْمُرْتَضٰى وَفَاطِمَةَ الزَّهْرَاءِ وَخَدِيْجَةَ الْكُبْرٰى وَالْحَسَنِ الْمُجْتَبٰى وَالْحُسَيْنِ الشَّهِيْدِ بِكَرْبَلَاءَ، وَعَلٰى عَلِيِّ بْنِ الْحُسَيْنِ زَيْنِ الْعَابِدِيْنَ وَمُحَمَّدِ بْنِ عَلِيٍّ الْبَاقِرِ وَجَعْفَرِ بْنِ مُحَمَّدٍ الصَّادِقِ وَمُوْسَى بْنِ جَعْفَرِ", "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": " نِ", "ArabicText3": "الْكَاظِمِ وَعَلِيِّ بْنِ مُوْسَى الرِّضَا وَمُحَمَّدِ بْنِ عَلِيِّ", "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": " نِ", "ArabicText4": "التَّقِيِّ وَعَلِيِّ بْنِ مُحَمَّدٍ النَّقِيِّ وَالْحَسَنِ بْنِ عَلِيِّ", "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": " نِ", "ArabicText5": "الْعَسْكَرِيِّ وَالْحُجَّةِ الْقَاۗئِمِ الْمَهْدِيِّ الْاِمَامِ الْمُنْتَظَرِ صَلَوَاتُ اللهِ عَلَيْهِمْ اَجْمَعِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010053, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Dost rakh usey jo unhe dost rakhe, aur dushmani rakh us se jo un se dushmani rakhe, aur madad kar uski jo unki madad kare, aur chhod de unko aur laanat kar un par jo zulm kare, aur Aale Muhammad (a.s) ko kushaadgi dene mein jaldi kar, aur Aale Muhammad (a.s) ke shiyyo’n ki madad farma, aur mujhe Qaaem'e Aale Muhammad (a.t.f.s) ka didaar naseeb farma, aur mujh ko unke paiyro-kaaro’n aur unke madad-gaaro’n aur unke kaam se khoosh hone waalo’n mein qaraar de apni rehmat se, ay sab se ziyadah rahem karne waale.", "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA WAALE MAN WALAA-HUM WA AA’DE MAN AA’DAA-HUM WANSUR MAN NASARA-HUM WAKH-ZUL MAN KHA-ZALA-HUM WAL-A’N MAN ZALA-MA-HUM WA A’JJIL FARAJA AALE MOHAMMADIN WANSUR SHEE-A’TA AALE MOHAMMADIN (WA AH-LIK A’DAA-A AALE MOHAMMADIN) WAR-ZUQNEE ROO-YATA QAA'e ME AALE MOHAMMADIN WAJ-A’L-NEE MIN ATBAA-E’HI WA ASH-YAA-E’HI WARRAA-ZEENA BE-FE’LEHI BE-RAH-MATE-KA YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ وَالِ مَنْ وَالَاهُمْ وَعَادِ مَنْ عَادَاهُمْ وَانْصُرْ مَنْ نَصَرَهُمْ وَاخْذُلْ مَنْ خَذَلَهُمْ وَالْعَنْ مَنْ ظَلَمَهُمْ وَعَجِّلْ فَرَجَ آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَانْصُرْ شِيْعَةَ آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ (وَاَهْلِكْ اَعْدَاۗءَ آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ) وَارْزُقْنِيْ رُؤْيَةَ قَاۗئِمِ آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَاجْعَلْنِيْ مِنْ اَتْبَاعِهٖ وَاَشْيَاعِهٖ